<p>Hi there</p>

<p>You signed up for Pagecord in <%= @blog.created_at.strftime("%B") %>, but it looks like you haven't had a chance to set things up yet.</p>

<p>A good place to start is:</p>

<ul>
  <li>pick a colour scheme and typeface</li>
  <li>add custom CSS if you want to take things further</li>
  <li>create a home page, About page, or Now page</li>
</ul>

<p>You don't need to finish everything in one go. Even a small bit of setup makes the blog feel much more like your own.</p>

