                <%= link_to "Start setting up your blog", app_onboarding_url %>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>If you'd prefer, you can ignore all that and just publish something small. A few sentences is enough.</p>

<p>Reply to this email if you want a hand. I'm happy to help.</p>

